BBQ Blitz - Season 1, Episode 3




Texas Takedown

Food Network Star winner Eddie Jackson heads back to where it all started for him, both on the field and in the kitchen: his hometown of Dallas! He's pitting some of Texas's best chefs and pit masters against one another, and celebrity judges chef John Tesar and former Dallas Cowboy Ken "The Hammer" Hamlin are on hand to decide who will win the $5,000 prize and reign supreme.




Original Air Date: 23-Oct-2015
